<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IAS21_3" principles="yes"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>3</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 21"/><data name="paranum" value="3"/></prolog><body outputclass="bold"><variant base="SL30913" id="IAS21_3_V2"> <p id="IAS21_P0012">This Standard shall be applied:<xref keyref="footnotes/IAS21_FN0002" type="fn"/></p> <ol outputclass="static" base="SL147515" id="IAS21_L0002" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="SL147517" id="IAS21_P0013">in accounting for transactions and balances in foreign currencies, except for those derivative transactions and balances that are within the scope of <xref base="F43753457" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_TOC.dita#IFRS09_TOC0001" id="IAS21_X0033">IFRS 9 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Financial Instruments</ph></ph></xref>; </p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="SL147519" id="IAS21_P0014">in translating the results and financial position of foreign operations that are included in the financial statements of the entity by consolidation or the equity method; and</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p base="SL147521" id="IAS21_P0015">in translating an entity’s results and financial position into a presentation currency.</p></li></ol></variant></body></paragraph>